@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Báo cáo AI";
}

<section class="page-header">
    <div><span class="eyebrow"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-bar-graph"></i> Reports</span><h1>Báo cáo & xuất dữ liệu</h1><p>Tạo báo cáo tài chính, ngân sách, KPI/OKR, performance ranking và executive summary bằng AI.</p></div>
    <button class="btn-app" data-demo-toast><i class="bi bi-magic"></i> Sinh báo cáo AI</button>
</section>

<section class="module-grid">
    <article class="module-card"><i class="bi bi-graph-up"></i><h3>Financial overview</h3><p>Thu/chi, utilization, cash runway, budget variance.</p></article>
    <article class="module-card"><i class="bi bi-wallet"></i><h3>Budget utilization</h3><p>So sánh phòng ban, danh mục, cảnh báo vượt ngưỡng.</p></article>
    <article class="module-card"><i class="bi bi-bullseye"></i><h3>KPI/OKR status</h3><p>Progress, confidence, blockers và next actions.</p></article>
    <article class="module-card"><i class="bi bi-award"></i><h3>Performance ranking</h3><p>Điểm tổng, rating, nhân viên cần coaching.</p></article>
</section>

<article class="panel mt-3">
    <div class="panel-header"><h2 class="panel-title"><i class="bi bi-file-text"></i> Executive summary Q2/2026</h2><div class="toolbar"><button class="btn-ghost"><i class="bi bi-filetype-pdf"></i> PDF</button><button class="btn-ghost"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-excel"></i> Excel</button></div></div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        <p><strong>Tóm tắt:</strong> Doanh thu đang tăng 12.4%, nhưng chi phí Marketing vượt ngân sách Digital Ads 21%. KPI trung bình đạt 72%, trong đó Sales pipeline cần can thiệp trong 2 tuần tới.</p>
        <div class="three-col-grid mt-3">
            <div class="list-item"><div><strong>Top risk</strong><small>Marketing overspend</small></div><span class="status-badge danger">High</span></div>
            <div class="list-item"><div><strong>Opportunity</strong><small>Lead conversion vượt target</small></div><span class="status-badge success">Good</span></div>
            <div class="list-item"><div><strong>Action</strong><small>Khóa PR ads mới</small></div><span class="status-badge info">Next</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</article>
